OL,3,CMan jailed for 16-months after killing
OL,4,Cschoolgirl at pedestrian crossing
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for 16-months
OL,7,Fafter killing a 15-year-old girl at a
OL,8,Fpedestrian crossing.
OL,10,FChristopher West, 42, hit Keely Morgan
OL,11,Fwith his Vauxhall Astra on Heol
OL,12,FTrelai, Caerau, Cardiff at about
OL,13,F9.30pm on May 1 2023. She sadly died
OL,14,Fat the scene.
OL,16,FCardiff Crown Court heard that West's
OL,17,Ftwo daughters and their friend had
OL,18,Fbeen in the car during the incident.
