OL,3,CMan jailed for 16-months after killing
OL,4,Cschoolgirl at pedestrian crossing
OL,6,FWest, who was driving over the 30mph
OL,7,Fspeed limit, failed to see the
OL,8,Fteenager, despite her being lit up by
OL,9,Fan iPad she had been using at the
OL,10,Fpedestrian crossing.
OL,12,FKeely had overcome significant health
OL,13,Fproblems ahead of her death, having
OL,14,Fundergone a kidney transplant in 2021
OL,15,Fto save her life.
OL,17,FOne of the passengers told the police
OL,18,FWest had been "snaking" along the road
OL,19,Fand had removed his car's black box,
OL,20,Finvalidating his insurance, to show
OL,21,Foff to them.
