OL,3,CMan jailed for 16-months after killing
OL,4,Cschoolgirl at pedestrian crossing
OL,6,FWest, from Ely, previously pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to causing death by dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving and causing death while
OL,9,Funinsured.
OL,11,FHowever, the defendant initially
OL,12,Fclaimed the car's black box had been
OL,13,Fdisconnected while he was working on
OL,14,Fthe car, and he had forgotten to
OL,15,Freconnect it and his driving had been
OL,16,Fnormal. His passengers said that was
OL,17,Fnot correct.
