OL,3,CMan jailed for 16-months after killing
OL,4,Cschoolgirl at pedestrian crossing
OL,6,FJudge Paul Hobson branded West as an
OL,7,F"irresponsible show off" at a
OL,8,Fsentencing hearing on Thursday, July
OL,9,F27.
OL,11,F"Keely Morgan was just 15-years-old
OL,12,Fwhen she died on May 1 2023," he said.
OL,14,F"Keely died as a result of your
OL,15,Factions, as a result of your careless
OL,16,Fdriving that evening."
OL,18,FHe added: "You should have seen her
OL,19,Fand come to a stop in order to allow
OL,20,Fher to cross.
