OL,3,CMan jailed for 16-months after killing
OL,4,Cschoolgirl at pedestrian crossing
OL,6,FWest had been described as
OL,7,F"apologetic" and in a state of panic
OL,8,Fafter the collision. But the judge
OL,9,Fsaid: "Any remorse that you have is
OL,10,Fovershadowed by your attempts to
OL,11,Fminimise your level of responsibility,
OL,12,Fto the extent of challenging what your
OL,13,Fown passengers were saying.
OL,15,F"Although you may well be sorry for
OL,16,Fwhat happened to Keely, a large part
OL,17,Fof your concern is for yourself."
